  "texts": [
    "Second, students' negative attitudes toward AI was found to be another prevailing challenge.",
    "Negative attitudes encompassed concerns about negative side effects of GenAI-assisted writing and potential adverse consequences or unintended outcomes of GenAI such as biases and errors.",
    "As seen from P6 quotes in Appendix 4, students' negative attitude toward AI could cause reluctance to fully engage with AIassisted tasks, and limit the potential uses of AI in the writing tasks process.",
    "Third, the lack of higher-order thinking has emerged as a barrier in GenAIassisted writing.",
    "For instance, students faced challenges in critically evaluating AI-generated content, formulating logical arguments, and engaging in nuanced reasoning on AI-generated content."
  ],
